@m36dot aren't the old positions correct?
In L34 we have the error in details,
private static final String INVALID_RESOURCE_PARAMETERS =
            "invalid resource parameter(s): cannot specify > 2 parameters without specifying path config and/or body " +
                    "config in the resource annotation";

So I feel position should be the position of annotation. Not function def start.
I fixed this to get annotation positions.

